featured_reviews.review_id: Mattannur juma masjid. Very beautiful masjid located on the heart of mattannur, KANNUR.  Very useful for travellers and passengers. Nearly renowned but maintenance was poor. No water tap working for ablution, no bulb working in bathroom, etc showing lack of maintenance fund or corruption probability. Other plus points are large place for pray for travelling womens and well maintained bathrooms. Have ample car parking place but entry was narrow for two cars same time.
